  <h2>Common Seed-Starting Situations</h2>

  <div class="scenarioGrid">
    <div class="scenarioCard">
      <h3>Peppers in a Cool Basement</h3>
      <p>
        A thermostat is usually worth it here. Peppers benefit from steady warmth, and cool basement conditions make temperature control more useful.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="scenarioCard">
      <h3>Tomatoes in a Normal Heated Room</h3>
